ygData.subject: Re: Digest Number 67
ygData.msgSnippet: Yah, the ranger armor is high on my list when I feel competent enough to go get Meldrath s head... say, ten levels or so down the road. =)  Haven t seen it,
ygData.messageBody:
Yah, the ranger armor is high on my list when I feel competent enough to go get
Meldrath's head... say, ten levels or so down the road. =) Haven't seen it,
though, but I've seen the bard and the warrior, so I'm looking forward to the
ranger's. I also saw red, but it was on an anonymous player, so I have no idea
what class that's for... a very vivid red, like a ruby (no, I don't believe it
was Rubicite).

>
> Catt, High Elf Paladin, E'ci
